schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
# Type definition

type Auth {
    token: String
    message: String
}

type User {
    _id: ID
    first_name: String
    last_name: String
    username: String
    profile_biography: String
    profile_image_url: String
    email: String
    is_active: Boolean
}

# Input Fields

input UserCreateInput {
    first_name: String!
    last_name: String!
    username: String!
    profile_biography: String
    profile_image_url: String
    email: String!
    password: String!
}

# Queries

type Query {
    User(id: ID!): User
    Users:[User]
}

# Mutations 

type Mutation {
    signup(data: UserCreateInput!): Auth
}
